        <p>Outdated panel replacement and capacity upgrades. 100A to 200A upgrades, fuse box conversions, sub-panel installation, and meter base replacement.</p>
        <span class="service-card-link">Learn More <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></span>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/lighting-installation/" class="service-card">
